<section id="sample" class="section bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 relative">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row">
        <!-- Image Section -->
        <div class="md:w-2/5 relative">
          <img 
            src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1629781/pexels-photo-1629781.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600" 
            alt="Dog with Forest Calm products" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/70 to-transparent flex items-end">
            <div class="p-6 text-white">
              <h3 class="text-2xl mb-2 text-white">免費體驗 Forest Calm</h3>
              <p class="text-accent">讓您的毛孩感受天然的溫柔呵護。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Form Section -->
        <div class="md:w-3/5 p-6 md:p-8">
          <h2 class="text-primary text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4">想免費體驗？填問卷送你一份！</h2>
          
          <p class="mb-6">
            填寫簡單問卷，告訴我們你的毛孩體質，即可免費索取 Forest Calm 洗毛精體驗包！
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-accent/50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2">常見問題</h4>
            <details class="mb-3">
              <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">Forest Calm 的洗毛精適合所有毛孩嗎？</summary>
              <p class="mt-2 pl-4 text-gray-600">
                Forest Calm 特別為敏感體質毛孩設計，配方溫和、低刺激，大多數犬種皆適用。若毛孩有嚴重皮膚問題，建議先諮詢獸醫後使用。
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="mb-3">
              <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">無香款真的完全沒有香味嗎？</summary>
              <p class="mt-2 pl-4 text-gray-600">
                是的，Pure Calm 無香舒敏款完全不添加人工香精與精油，只保留植物原生的微弱氣味，給極敏毛孩最純淨、最安心的呵護。
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="mb-3">
              <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">森林香氛款會不會對敏感毛孩太刺激？</summary>
              <p class="mt-2 pl-4 text-gray-600">
                Forest Gentle 森林香氛款只添加極少量天然精油（如薰衣草、雪松、佛手柑），配方經特別調整，溫和低敏，適合一般敏感體質毛孩。如果毛孩極度敏感，建議優先選擇無香款。
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="mb-3">
              <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">你們的產品是在哪裡製造的？</summary>
              <p class="mt-2 pl-4 text-gray-600">
                Forest Calm 全系列產品皆由台灣在地研發、製造，並且嚴選成分來源，確保品質安全、成分透明。
              </p>
            </details>
            <details>
              <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">可以天天幫毛孩洗澡嗎？</summary>
              <p class="mt-2 pl-4 text-gray-600">
                若使用 Forest Calm 的天然溫和配方，一般情況下一週洗 1–2 次已足夠。天天洗澡可能會影響毛孩皮膚天然油脂平衡，建議視季節、活動量及獸醫建議調整頻率。
              </p>
            </details>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center">
            <a 
              href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeZHgG1xxpLvwtAtqHhAuG7Wv7CuFkOaqTkBdoLwAcOzLWEyw/viewform?usp=header" 
              target="_blank" 
              rel="noopener noreferrer" 
              class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" />
              </svg>
              點我填問卷
            </a>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-3">
              *每人限領一份，數量有限，送完為止
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-16 h-16 bg-primary/20 rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/3 right-1/3 w-24 h-24 bg-secondary/20 rounded-full"></div>
</section>